<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV35">
<l>pālvāyp piṟaippiḷḷai yokkalaik koṇṭu pakaliḻanta</l>
<l>mēlpāṟ ṟicaippeṇ pulampuṟu mālai yulakaḷanta</l>
<l>mālpāṟ ṟuḻāykku maṉamuṭai yārkkunal kiṟṟaiyellāñ</l>
<l>cōlvāṉ pukuntitu vōrpaṉi vāṭai tuḻākiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Evening, when the woman of the western direction is lonely</l>
<l>who has lost the day, taking on [her] hip the milk-mouthed crescent moon child,</l>
<l>is this, entering to seize all that had been granted to those whose mind is on</l>
<l>the Tulsi by Māl who measured the world. A chilly north wind stirs.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
